UID:69bd696fe2a2952aed097dca@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Every other Saturday Cliffcrest will be screening a free famil
 y friendly movie!\nThis month's movie:\nPiece by Piece\nA unique cinematic
