 n turned into a world of eternal winter by the evil White Witch. Aided by 
 the wise lion Aslan\, the children lead Narnia into a climactic battle to 
 rid the land of the Witch's glacial powers forever. 2h 29m with a short in
 termission. Drop-in\, no registration necessary.
