 et new people at the library. Games available for use in the Children's Ar
 ea.\nAvailable games include: Ball Fall Jumbo (Ages 3+)\, STEM Pretend Flo
 wer Garden Toy Set (Ages 3-6)\, Operation (Ages 6+)\, STEM Road Builder 
 Game (Ages 4-8)\, Dinosaur Tetra Tower Balance Stacking Blocks Game (Ages
  6+)\nAvailable puzzles include: Giant World Map Puzzle (Ages 4+)\, Cana
 da Map Jigsaw Puzzle (Ages 4-12)\, ABC Puzzle (Ages 3+)
LOCATION:Mimico Centennial
