DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260426T150000
UID:69879b884a9fd98b7f7cb6d7@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Craft\, create\, and have fun -- perfect for kids 6+ and their
  families!\nPlease register only the children who will be participating in
  the craft. Adults do not need to register.\nMarch 1 - Caterpillar Pen Hol
 der\nMarch 8 - Leprechaun House\nMarch 15 - Leprechaun Mask\nMarch 22 - 
 Easter Bunny Craft\nMarch 29 - Mini Easter Basket\nApril 12 - Umbrella Cra
 ft\nApril 19 - Gnome's Garden\nApril 26 - Book Vase and Flowers
LOCATION:Mimico Centennial\, Auditorium
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69879b884a9fd98b7f7cb6d7
X-SOURCE:Toronto Public Library
END:VEVENT
