DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260428T180000
UID:69b2f1b71e64afd01e61a3dd@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Turn pages of old discarded books into works of art in this mi
 x media workshop. Learn to create drawings and paintings of botanical obje
 cts such as flowers and berries in pen and watercolour.\nThis is a drop-in
  program. Spaces are limited.\nThis program is part of Youth Hub service. 
 Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens after school and in the summer\
 , where helpful staff are always available. Free\, nutritious snacks are 
 offered daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call the branch to 
 find out more.
