 rtist Hina Yasir! Hina will do a deep dive into the history and art of hen
 na designs\, and then demonstrate popular henna techniques. Participants w
 ill be able to use cones of real henna to create designs.\nThis program is
  part of Youth Hub service. Youth Hubs are a welcoming place for teens aft
 er school and in the summer\, where helpful staff are always available. F
