DESCRIPTION:Join us for an interactive\, movement-based program where we r
 ead stories and make them come alive with our bodies! Join Megan Snider\, 
 author and Founder of Appleseed Yoga for Kids as she delivers inspiring st
 ories and gets the whole family moving. Class begins and ends with song an
 d breath work and is filled with pages of creativity and activity. Kids an
 d families can sit quietly and listen\, do partial poses or make up their 
 own\, following our lead. It's ALL yoga! No experience\, mats\, or materia
 ls required.\nThis program is intended for children aged 0 to 12 years and
  their families.
