DESCRIPTION:Create your own perler bead art! Follow a template or create y
 our own designs. You can even transform it into a keychain! Bring a friend
  or two and explore your creativity.\nFor ages 6 – 12 years old. Drop in
 \, no registration required. Space is limited.\nInformation Collection Not
 ice:\nThe personal information on this form is collected by the Toronto Pu
 blic Library under the Public Libraries Act\, sections 20(a)\, 20(c)\, and
  20(d). The information will only be used for event and program registrati
 on\, delivery\, and evaluation. Questions about how the library handles yo
 ur information can be directed to Answerline staff at answerline@tpl.ca\, 
 416-397-5981\, 789 Yonge Street\, Toronto ON M4W 2G8.
LOCATION:Thorncliffe\, Program Room-Second Floor
URL:https://tpl.bibliocommons.com/v2/events/69c4585e2866a5b488446ad3
