DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260412T140000
UID:699f449a6583d22e3c0d2bd6@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Would you like to learn to crochet? Join us for this 4 session
  class to learn a few basic stitches that we'll then use to create a croc
 heted\, stuffed keychain pendant.  All supplies will be provided.\nPlease
  secure your spot by registering.
