BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Youth Hub: Gaming Night
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T154500
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20260415T180000
UID:69b8380a403a4e5652df5488@tpl.bibliocommons.com
DESCRIPTION:Join us every in the youth hub for our video game night. Teens
  can play on the   Nintendo Switch or PS5. Choose from a variety of games 
 and play with friends!\nThis program is part of Youth Hub service. Youth H
 ubs are a welcoming place for teens after school and in the summer\, where
  helpful staff are always available. Free\, nutritious snacks are offered
  daily. Drop by a branch with a\nYouth Hub\nor call the branch to find ou
 t more.
