 our grading techniques to give your videos a consistent and professional l
 ook.\nWork with audio by adjusting levels\, removing background noise\, an
 d adding effects to improve overall sound quality. You’ll also learn how
  to balance music\, dialogue\, and sound effects within your project.\nBy 
